Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想要說些漂亮的話麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好 還剩下一邊的鏡片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂宛如身經百戰的勇士一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這勇士還真脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立花美里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己做了錯事 我還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.78,STAFF,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H3E3E3E&}剛\N起\N步\N就
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得啊 那樣果然是行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人看著！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要死了！！ 要死了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直要害羞死了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是我弄壞了他的眼鏡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得做笹原的眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係哦 沒關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要說一下「這傢伙眼鏡壞了」 怎麼看這都是慈善事業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊… 不過是遵循志願精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天 我來做一下你的眼睛而已哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立花美里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換教室之前 我想去一趟廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廁所 難道是男廁所！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誠然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:04:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就來了障礙！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 畢竟是我錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰勝困難我們的關係才能越來越深厚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦！ 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你眼鏡壞了嘛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 觀察能力真差啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說今天你看不見 所以我來給笹原你做一天的眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎誤會什麼！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是偶然要將你右手腕上的一隻小蟲子慢慢按死而已哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是個大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:59.92,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\shad2\pos(510,360)\4c&HE4E1E1&}咖\N哩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鐮倉那有一家咖哩很辣的店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師能吃多辣的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我也是！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 長野原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要去上課…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要去上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LL教室沒在那邊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LL教室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看 那個啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清楚發生什麼了才是棒球 什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此才有趣 什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清楚發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是棒球…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 還不能認定那個人就是女朋友 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 說的對啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笹原學長他——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先回去吧 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:06:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長野原同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃你先去LL教室跟老師糊弄一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 要撞上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美… 美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美 美緒！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 美緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:07:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美 美緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美 美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞你妹啊——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緒 緒美！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緒… 緒美！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝… 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小馬！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 沒事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還算好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧這個人救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 那可是叫作妨礙公務執行的罪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說你們是連我也算上了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該跟學校聯絡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看在這件事的面子上就不追究了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了啊 梳辮子的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了剛才的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然靈光一閃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要試試用拳擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,征服世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶 搶東西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別恨我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走一步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過後來一趟局裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你表彰的日程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治蟲 可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 冷靜下來之後來一趟事務所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後詳談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒的英語教科書不知道什麼時候沒了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是告白之前就被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是全力奔跑的途中救了個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是表彰、得到了個風箏、被拳擊手相中什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 都弄不清楚發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像小祐說的那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清楚發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是棒球 對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 你說神馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}隻{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:57.15,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\frz8\pos(555,276)\c&H78707B&}年糕小豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空想什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不花錢的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從學校就開始緊緊的跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是一下子沒看見 就一瞬間不知不覺的消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的高性能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可讓我更想知道你的秘密了啊 東雲名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 既然來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找一下像那樣的家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 緊追不捨也是有危險的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天再跟蹤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是完全暴露了嘛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然一下子找到了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是開展東雲捕獲作戰以來最幸運的一刻了嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這可不是幸運這種詞彙能夠衡量的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說什麼呢 那個 什麼呢 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種興奮的心情是怎麼回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻就像進房間一覽這個研究室！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要見見製造東雲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要把設計圖搶過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這高漲的期待造成的悸動在我全身流竄！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜啊 我心中的「牛仔」比爾沃茨！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}比爾沃茨：前美國職業摔角手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說畢竟是製造東雲的人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道會有什麼陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不能意氣用事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啦 今天就先偷窺一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問您有何貴幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾內亞！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就被偵查用機器人發現了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然外表看起來挺廉價的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是跟製造東雲一樣高的技術的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個不小心可不清楚會被怎樣！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 一定不能抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 中村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾內亞！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是嚇得我渾身癱軟啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說多虧那個才能侵入這個家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不能完全放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假設這裡有陷阱是比較妥當的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說這杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認定這裡有消除一時記憶的藥肯定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且說不定 在這個房間的某個角落裡有雙監視的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什什什什什 什麼啊那貨！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個形勢明顯有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說看起來像是雜亂無章的放在那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也不得不感受得到一種在某處瞄著我的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是馬虎了的話 這貨…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會幹掉我啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您 您怎麼了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  抱歉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事也沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝下去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太糟了 我竟然做出這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}啊 是太燙了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正要被幹掉了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就單刀直入的講了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒！？ 啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更加深入瞭解東雲而來這裡的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話我想看一下真實的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得那是個人的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得都是女孩子大家交往還是很不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情果然還是普通的最好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！ 不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全錯了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想些什麼呢啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知廉恥的傢伙啊 你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉！！萬分抱歉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想深入瞭解的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}名乃 零食吃沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 她是說「博士」了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}不行哦 明天再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該只是我聽錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是這個孩子製造的東雲這種事是不可能的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}這個人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子是東雲的親屬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}是學校的中村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話這個孩子也是機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我製造了名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肩部撞擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}博… 博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製造了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}為什麼要說出來啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將東雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}因為要打招呼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給我做些什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這小鬼又做了些什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人造人！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面的偵查機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題的不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東雲名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我承認徒手又滿不在乎的就進來是我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這個家相當的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}博士 你這是什麼結啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要趕緊抓個空當快跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能重新思考作戰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}緊緊結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}哦誒 小姑娘 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕那貨來襲擊我 恐懼纏身不敢亂動…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坦率的說「我要回去」什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去一下 廁所嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我帶你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要告訴我地方的話 我一個人也能去！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徹底上當了啊 東雲名乃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的成功脫逃啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會就那麼信了我的話的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 你的弱點就是人太好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在這個地方吹起對抗你的風的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好等著吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你的那個弱點不消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論多少次我都會復活！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 您要回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 那什麼 哪個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們… 拜託我護理一下草坪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等… 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要露餡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連我要逃跑這種事情都全部看破了嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 這是什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體…！ 身體的自由…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 但是她說要去廁所來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個漿糊 用水就可以弄掉吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是在這裡被捕獲了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}什麼～～～？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就全都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}水啊 水～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的野心 我生存的意義就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}什麼～～？ 聽不見啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要趕緊做些什麼 將這個狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}把我這個解開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東雲研究所！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}水！ 水！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}我應該做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我啊——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我帶著那個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼？ 那可以拜託你麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 下次記得帶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說「搞不清楚發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那就是棒球」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 突然就笑了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在勉強裝沒事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是失戀於一直傾慕著的學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不是看不出來那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是說哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小祐你又忘了作業了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但確實忘記作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案 廣告之後告訴你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真有趣啊 相生同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 水上同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫累銘定則？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饒舌？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長野原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想順便拜託你一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學 還有什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鼓勵一下長野原同學方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易準備跟小祐她們去吃點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請抽獎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小祐吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小祐？ 那是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都完全露餡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 發條都看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才不是什麼機器人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 通過這裡的人必須要抽一下獎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉一轉就行了吧？
